{
  "texts": [
    "Sentiment analysis represents one of the most prevalent use cases of automated text analysis in marketing, offering deep insights into consumer emotions, opinions, and perceptions [26,30].",
    "Applications of sentiment analysis include generating market insights from user-generated online content [45], predicting virality from linguistic features of newspaper articles [3], or identifying top performing individuals by analyzing the language style used in emails [67].",
    "The field of sentiment analysis employs diverse methods, ranging from lexicon-based approaches to traditional machine learning models, and extending to the more advanced transfer learning techniques, as detailed by Hartmann et al.",
    "(2019 Hartmann et al.",
    "( & 2023)) [24,25]."
  ]
}